                            <comment id="195139" author="adilger" created="Tue, 9 May 2017 17:33:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This just looks like fallout from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9096&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_253: File creation failed after rm&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-9096&quot;&gt;LU-9096&lt;/a&gt;. If there are no instances of this test failing without test_253 failing first then please close this ticket as a duplicate. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="194509" author="casperjx" created="Thu, 4 May 2017 22:20:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6008&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_102b: setstripe failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6008&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6008&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: sanity test_102b: setstripe failed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
